HB 893 Original 2026 Regular Session Knox
Abstract: Provides relative to the purchase of materials and supplies by the Sewerage and
Water Board of New Orleans.
Present law provides that the public water system, public sewerage system, and public
drainage system of the city of New Orleans shall be constructed, controlled, maintained, and
operated by a sewerage and water board. Provides for the composition of the board and its
powers and duties.
Proposed law retains present law.
